&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are seeking a dedicated and detail-oriented Business Analyst to join our team, specializing in Change Management and Change Enablement to join our Transformation Programme Office within the IT Group. In this role, you will work closely with cross-functional product teams to assess, design, and implement effective change strategies that ensure the smooth transition of on-premise systems to evergreen cloud-based products, coupled with product management operating model. Your ability to analyze our organization needs and translate them into actionable plans will be key to driving successful change initiatives, fostering stakeholder engagement, and ensuring readiness for change.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
